data.description: With just under one acre of land, this property offers the perfect balance of privacy and community, providing a rural retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life while still being within a few miles of shopping, medical & schools. Built in 2004, this 3400 sqft, 4 bedroom, plus 2 office spaces, 3 bath home overlooks the Snake River! Imagine having morning coffee or dinner guests on the expansive deck with the river and hills teeming with wildlife as your backdrop. Additional amenities include 2 gas fireplaces, walk-out basement well suited for entertaining in the large family room with coffee/drink bar, a 2 car garage, spacious yard with curbing for easy mowing and an automatic sprinkler system.
